    rdfs:label "Emeishan Traps (峨眉山暗色岩 Éméishān ànsèyán)"@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://metadatahub.eu/data/geologic-timescale> ;
    skos:definition "Large igneous province in southwestern China (Sichuan, Yunnan, Guizhou); ~0.5 million km²; linked to Capitanian/end-Guadalupian extinction event; preceded Siberian Traps by ~8 Myr."@en ;
